entry.string: Loading image into kind cluster: trading-cluster
kind load docker-image hmm-model-training-dev:dev-7-77e6fb9 --name trading-cluster kind load docker-image hmm-model-training-dev:dev-latest --name trading-cluster
kubectl create namespace trading-monitoring-dev --context kind-trading-cluster 2>/dev/null || echo "Namespace trading-monitoring-dev already exists"
